'''Abdul Aziz Khan''' (dates unknown) was an Indian [[first-class cricket]]er active 1912–1926 who played mostly for the [[Muslims cricket team]]. He made eleven appearances, scoring 185 [[run (cricket)|runs]] with a highest score of 43, and took 18 [[wicket]]s with a best [[innings]] return of five for 79.<ref name=CA>[https://cricketarchive.com/Archive/Players/38/38009/38009.html Abdul Aziz Khan at CricketArchive]</ref><ref name=CI>[http://www.espncricinfo.com/india/content/player/26591.html Abdul Aziz Khan at ESPNcricinfo]</ref>

