'''Abu Abdallah V''' (ruled 1504–1517) was a Sultan of the [[Kingdom of Tlemcen]] in [[Algeria]].<ref>{{cite book| first1=Nagendra Kr| last1=Singh| first2=Nagendra Kumar| last2=Singh| title=International Encyclopaedia of Islamic Dynasties| year=2000| publisher=Anmol Publications| place=New Delhi| ISBN=8126104031}}</ref> He was a son of [[Abu Abdallah IV]].

